name: R3_v2_0550_for_R5
title: Cross-version VS for R3.v2 Body Parts for use in FHIR R5
description: This cross-version ValueSet represents concepts from http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/v2-0550|2.8.2 for use in FHIR R5. Concepts not present here have direct `equivalent` mappings crossing all versions from R3 to R5.
